

This project's goal is to evaluate whether certain demographics can influence the AI tool a developer would use.

Gotten from the Stack Overflow 2024 Survey, this dataset contain a high amount of specific developer information.

Multiple hypothesis tests were ran to verify the demographical associaction to AI tool use
    results:
        Age-AI tool: associated
        Education level- AI tool: associated
        DEveloper Role-AI tool: associated
        Years coding professionally-AI tool: at least one instance is associated